      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a Time Sliding Window Three Colour Marker (TSWTCM), which can be used as a component in a Diff-Serv traffic conditioner.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
